

## Drawable Resources Naming Conventions
When naming custom drawables, use the following naming conventions:
1. Use lowercase letters.
2. Separate words with an underscore.
3. Use the following format: `type_description_optionalState` e.g. `btn_submit_disabled`
4. Use the following types:
    - `btn` for buttons
    - `ic` for icons
    - `bg` for backgrounds
    - `divider` for dividers
    - `selector` for selectors
    - `shape` for shapes
    - `state` for states
    - `list` for list items
    - `tab` for tabs
    - `indicator` for indicators
    - `progress` for progress bars
    - `dialog` for dialogs
    - `popup` for popups
    - `menu` for menus
    - `card` for cards
    - `chip` for chips
    - `avatar` for avatars
    - `badge` for badges
    - `indicator` for indicators
    - `switch` for switches
    - `checkbox` for checkboxes
    - `radio` for radio buttons
    - `edittext` for edit texts
    - `spinner` for spinners
    - `slider` for sliders
    - `seekbar` for seekbars
    - `ratingbar` for rating bars
    - `progressbar` for progress bars
    - `calendar` for calendars
    - `datepicker` for date pickers
    - `timepicker` for time pickers
    - `search` for search views
    - `toolbar` for toolbars
    - `navigation` for navigation views
    - `bottomnavigation` for bottom navigation views
    -  `bottomsheet` for bottom sheets
    - `navigationdrawer` for navigation drawers
    - `appbar` for app bars
    - `tablayout` for tab layouts
    - `viewpager` for view pagers
    - `recyclerview` for recycler views
    - `listview` for list views
    - `gridview` for grid views
    - `scrollview` for scroll views
    - `nestedscrollview` for nested scroll views
    - `webview` for web views
    - `imageview` for image views
    - `textview` for text views
    - `button` for buttons
    - `edittext` for edit texts
    - `checkbox` for checkboxes
    - `radiobutton` for radio buttons
    - `switch` for switches
    - `spinner` for spinners
    - `progressbar` for progress bars
    - `seek` for seek bars
    - `rating` for rating bars
    - `calendar` for calendars
    - `datepicker` for date pickers
